{"type":null,"faqId":33549,"title":"为什么听音乐时发热？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-family:Arial;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">全高清手机在亮屏幕听音乐的时候手感稍热，在天气较热的时候会比正常室温下热感受明显，这些是业界普遍现象，手机本身并无质量问题，您可以放心使用。</span><span class=\"s2\">本手机对音乐播放音质进行了提升，发热也会略有增加，请不要以大音量长时间外放音乐。另外，智</span><span class=\"s1\">能手机在听音乐同时下载音乐文件、对手机进行划屏等复合操作时，会造成手机额外的耗电与发热，比单纯听音乐时候稍热。请尽量避免同时在听音乐的时候下载音乐，操作手机进行其他业务。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8269","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748653000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":19,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"发热,音乐","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}